sources.description:
BLAZING GUNS...HE-MAN ADVENTURE! 
Chasing jewel thieves, Captain Carson and Magpie head for the border where Carson, posing as a Chinaman, opens a store that buys jewelry. To flush the thieves into the open, Carson wins all.

Director: Sam Newfield
Writer: Isadore Bernstein 
Stars: Tim McCoy, Nora Lane, Ben Corbett 
Genres: Western
